name: My beating heart, shining through...
description:
This is my 50th artistic NFT, across all platforms, since I began this creative journey back in September of 2021. I'm still enjoying the artistic process, learning and developing as I go, and have enjoyed the people I've met in this incredibly vibrant and supportive community. Onward and upward from here, who knows where this road might lead.


720 X 720 px Animated Glitch PNG at 40 frames per second
